description:
Become a sorority sister in College Girl! Go shopping for hot fashion, go to the hottest frat parties, and date hot frat boys.  Build up your wardrobe by shopping at the most fashionable stores, then show off your glamorous new clothes at the hottest parties! Pursue your college dreams and become a sorority president! You'll have an exciting life in College Girl! 

- Customize your look with the hottest fashion. Go shopping at 5 different stores and choose from 350+ dresses, shirts, purses, shoes, and accessories!
- Visit the salon and get a makeover! Choose from over 20 different hair styles! Dye your hair with 8 possible colors!
- Tired from shopping all day? Visit the Cafe for an energy boost from coffee or an iced latte!
- Earn your place in the sorority and become the sorority president! 
- Hang out at the coolest frat parties and meet hot frat boys!
- Find a BOYFRIEND and go out on dates! Kiss your boyfriend and keep him happy!
- Enter into the FAME contest and show off your outfits to real players!
- Vote on other players outfits in the FAME section!

Follow us on Twitter: @dreamheartgames
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/dreamheartgames
Check out our website at: http://www.dreamheart.co
